item.description:
NOTICE *** Due to the Presidential Primary debates at St. A's being moved to Monday the 13th I have moved our meeting to Tuesday the 14th at 6:30 pm so Ovide can come and speak and so any that are wanting to watch or attend the Debates can do so. Please pass the word around.

New Hampshire's own Ovide Lamontagne the states only winner of the title Conservative of the Year since Senator George Lovejoy will be joining us to speak and answer our questions. Don't miss the opportunity to speak with Ovide.
item.name: NH Conservative of the Year Ovide Lamontagne to Speak
